## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="705e8-127">下列範例會建立應用程式會傳回服務匯流排相關資訊的文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-127">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="705e8-128">第一種方法， `GrammarUrlForRoute`，是一個字串，指定路由，並將它附加到字串，指定位置的文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-128">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="705e8-129">這會在該文法中指定特定規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-129">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="705e8-130">方法會傳回`Uri`該規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-130">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="705e8-131">第二種方法， `CreateGrammarForRoute`，建立<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>名`grammar`與所指定的規則參考`Uri`傳遞給它的`GrammarUrlForRoute`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-131">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="705e8-132">請注意，變數名稱 _route 封入類別的成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-132">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  
  
```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  
  
private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  
  
  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  
  
  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="705e8-133">名為 _ 變數`route`是未宣告和前一個範例中未定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-133">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="705e8-134">它應該宣告為<xref:System.String>和包含特定匯流排路由的路由號碼，才能編譯並執行先前的範例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="705e8-134">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>

  
  
